{"tid":531581,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"招高手教路上大阪環球影城","createTime":"2018-01-17T03:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T14:12:02.000Z","uid":9677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d012e350e0a235460817662f6077a661014db4","tid":531581,"uid":9677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"小弟7月頭去日本大阪環球影城有乜高招教下小弟,點樣可以又平又好玩<br />\n求各位巴打絲打教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3358edd98db6343a2293029f478b6fa663eab61e","tid":531581,"uid":15907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"想好玩就買fast pass"},{"pid":"680a9275ec8d848331952a05d45321ec5ffef2b6","tid":531581,"uid":9677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:20:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33a7a954919a79aaa8605395f61c3a80c549f31f","tid":531581,"uid":10342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:28:58.000Z","msg":"開場前早d去係門口排隊，等佢開門即刻跑去熱門設施，因為熱門設施真係勁多人排，冷門果d無咁多人自己衡量,玩足成日。<br />\n手帶無用，如果真係買就買快證<br />\n<br />\n盡量唔好星期六日夠熱門日子去，因為多人及海鮮價"},{"pid":"04176ab239cc9ff7067cf102553791aa8074abf7","tid":531581,"uid":15739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"8點幾去，一開始就入harry potter玩左先，其它設施可以扮一個人去，條隊快好多，而且可以同fd一齊坐，試過好多次<br />\n<br />\nbtw擲公仔唔好玩，伏黎"},{"pid":"784b7367db57f77ec6183607e5e1d1aca3ed32b7","tid":531581,"uid":154181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"十二月中去完 <br />\n手帶，Fp乜都冇買<br />\n朝早朝少少係門口等開門<br />\n一去即刻玩飛天翼龍先<br />\n其他野都唔洗點排<br />\n我個日星期五黎 唔算多人"},{"pid":"a4d825a1f7992285f1bd042a4034bba7be4c8f74","tid":531581,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"買翼龍快證已經夠 ，實夠時間玩曬"}]}